title: SEC Publishes Chair's Agenda - Finance and Banking - United States - Mondaq News Alerts
content: SEC Publishes Chair's Agenda - Finance and Banking - United States  Mondaq News Alerts
description: As required by the Regulatory Flexibility Act, the SEC published the Chair's agenda of rulemaking actions identifying rules the agency "expects to consider in the next 12 months that are likely to have a significant economic impact on a substantial number of small entities."
